(1) Cropsey Ave., south side, opposite Bay 11th Street, showing the Bennett homestead, also known as the Cortelyou house. In 1916 it was acquired by the Millrose Athletic Association for its Country home. Bay 11th Street, terminated at Cropsey Ave. in 1923; however the City has condemned this house, and is to continue Bay 11th Street to Warehouse Ave., on Gravesend Bay.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, showing the south side of the house.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3) The same, showing an easterly view.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(4) The same, showing the west side of the house.

March 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
